### Create Batch Payment - Continue Mode
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transactions/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payments": [
    {
      "recipientTag": "@user1",
      "amount": 100,
      "asset": "XLM",
      "memo": "Payment 1"
    },
    {
      "recipientTag": "@user2",
      "amount": 200,
      "asset": "XLM",
      "memo": "Payment 2"
    }
  ],
  "failureMode": "continue"
}

### Create Batch Payment - Abort Mode
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transactions/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payments": [
    {
      "recipientTag": "@user1",
      "amount": 100,
      "asset": "XLM",
      "memo": "Payment 1"
    },
    {
      "recipientTag": "@user2",
      "amount": 200,
      "asset": "XLM",
      "memo": "Payment 2"
    }
  ],
  "failureMode": "abort"
}

### Get Batch Payment Status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions/batch/1

### Large Batch Payment (50 payments)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transactions/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payments": [
    {"recipientTag": "@user1", "amount": 100, "asset": "XLM"},
    {"recipientTag": "@user2", "amount": 100, "asset": "XLM"},
    {"recipientTag": "@user3", "amount": 100, "asset": "XLM"},
    {"recipientTag": "@user4", "amount": 100, "asset": "XLM"},
    {"recipientTag": "@user5", "amount": 100, "asset": "XLM"},
    {"recipientTag": "@user6", "amount": 100, "asset": "XLM"},
    {"recipientTag": "@user7", "amount": 100, "asset": "XLM"},
    {"recipientTag": "@user8", "amount": 100, "asset": "XLM"},
    {"recipientTag": "@user9", "amount": 100, "asset": "XLM"},
    {"recipientTag": "@user10", "amount": 100, "asset": "XLM"}
  ],
  "failureMode": "continue"
}
